<div id="review_3762482865" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3762482865" />
    <a title="John Senner" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1981227-john-senner"><img alt="John Senner" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/m_50x66-82093808bca726cb3249a493fbd3bd0f.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3762482865?book_show_action=true">Jan 10, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="John Senner" class="user" itemprop="url" name="John Senner" href="/user/show/1981227-john-senner">John Senner</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was ok"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was ok</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9780679416494" href="/book/show/744291.Mexico">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3762482865" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer18132672817591138627">I liked Hawaii, so I was hopeful when I dug Mexico out of the shelf. Alas, not so good. Binational Norman Clay visits his old hometown to report on bull fights. He reprises the Indian, Spanish, and Virginia Confederate parts of his ancestry and how they came together in high plateau Mexican town with a silver mine. And lots of bull fights and behind the scenes of the whole business.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

